<h3>Actions</h3>
<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4>Travel</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>#: move that many states</li>
                <li>plane icon: move directly to any city</li>
                <li>[plane] + 1: move by plane and move 1 state, in either order</li>
                <li>DC is counted as a state for all game mechanisms</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Fundraise</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>take dollar amount on card</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Register</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>take X undecided voters into your personal supply</li>
                <li>undecided -> registered</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4>Advertise</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>pay $20m per issue</li>
                <li>must have enough registered voters for each state</li>
                <li>add exactly 1 registered voter to each state</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Campaign</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>pay $60m</li>
                <li>candidate pawn must be in one of the listed states</li>
                <li>add up to registered 6 voters, distributed among shaded states</li>
                <li>do not have to add to state with candidate pawn</li>
                <li>[home state icon]
                    <ul>
                        <li>pawn must be in <i>region</i> with home state</li>
                        <li>every state in the region is available for placement</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4>Politick</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>instant / ongoing / response</li>
                <li>after playing response, do not immediately refresh hand</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
